==English==
=== Adjective ===

#Without [[clouds]].
#:'''''Clear''' weather''
#[[Bright]], not [[dark]] or [[obscure]]d.
#:''The windshield was '''clear''' and clean.''
#Free of [[obstacle|obstacles]].
#Free of [[guilt]], or [[suspicion]].
#Free of [[ambiguity]] or [[doubt]].
#:''He gave '''clear''' instructions not to bother him at work.''

=== Translations ===
*German: [[klar]]
*[[Ido]]: [[klara]], [[evidenta]]
*[[Indonesian]]: [[jelas]], [[jernih]], [[bening]]
*Irish: [[glan]]
